metadata.name: Lord 1
metadata.description: Lords of Lyceum is a collection of 3,737 PFPs, hand-drawn and programmatically generated by snooplord. Each Lord's traits were selected from a pool of over 2,000 items. Each Lord is a citizen of a Cyber State of The Lyceum, has a foundational ideology, carries a book, and is assigned a VOICE score representing their voting power in The Lyceum Idea Market.
